Dynasty_Website_Product_Vision copy.md

# source logo art at the repo root (the site itself uses public/logos/, which
# stays tracked); anchored with "/" so it can't swallow public/logos on
# case-insensitive filesystems. Remove this line to version the source art.
/Logos/

# logs
npm-debug.log*
